Not to be outshined, an evasively anonymous summoner will not fess up to creating the LoL Swimsuit Studs. What a shame. We're looking forward to more submissions next week, so if something is new and exciting, send in a link and your Summoner Name to Summoner_Showcase@RiotGames.com!
